      <h2 class="highlighted blue">you're already travelling </h2>
      <h2 class="highlighted blue">then we've got you covered.</h2>
      <img src="//www.worldnomads.com/Media/Default/sta-travel/sta-travel-logo-colour.png" alt="STA TRAVEL" class="stalogo" />
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-5 large-5 columns left">
      <div id="stacalculator">
        <h1>Travel Insurance <br/>Simple &amp; Flexible</h1>
