<!-- Hero Content Panel Start -->
<div class="hero-content-panel part2" id="sta">
  <div class="row">  
    <div class="small-12 medium-12 large-12 columns">
      <h2 class="highlighted green">When should I buy</h2>
      <h2 class="highlighted green">travel insurance</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns">
      <p class="black">STA Travel has teamed up with World Nomads to provide cover for Non UK residents and travellers already overseas because:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns"></div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns clear">

      <ul class="tick">
        <li><span>If you're pre-booking flights, accommodation or tour activities and are worried about being well out of pocket if you need to unexpectedly cancel your trip.</span></li>
        <li><span>If you're concerned about having to cover large medical bills and organise your treatment overseas without the support of a 24/hr emergency assistance team.</span></li>
        <li><span>If you don't want the risk of having to pay upwards of USD $200,000 in evacuation costs should you get injured or seriously ill overseas.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns">
      <ul class="tick">
        <li><span>If you're worried about replacing your favourite tech such as laptops, digital cameras and iPads if they get stolen when travelling.</span></li>
        <li><span>If you want to have the flexibility to extend your cover should you choose to stay a little longer.</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="black">Having travel insurance in place gives you the peace of mind that if something does happen, you're covered!</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

